Class SETTINGS

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ufl.cise.SETTINGS

  • public class SETTINGS
extends java.lang.Object
    After each partial run (pause) you need to copy the log fiels generated at LOG_DIR to LOG_DIR_ARCHIVE to make sure they are not over written and are read so that the files that are already processed are skipped.

    morteza
